videos.headline: Day stops halftime interview amid clock confusion
videos.description: Ryan Day abruptly ends his halftime interview after the officials rule there is one second left on the clock, allowing Penn State to score a field goal.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Day stops halftime interview amid clock confusion) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dotson makes back-to-back one-handed grabs, scores TD
videos.description: Jahan Dotson grabs an impressive one-handed catch and makes magic again on the next play for a Penn State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Dotson makes back-to-back one-handed grabs, scores TD) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fields continues strong start to his season with 4 TDs in win
videos.description: Justin Fields continues his Heisman campaign as he throws for four touchdowns to help Ohio State take down Penn State in Happy Valley.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Fields continues strong start to his season with 4 TDs in win) 2020/10/31 ESHEET SOTFULL
